**In-Memory Features:**
- **Ultra-low Latency**: All data access from RAM
- **Non-Persistent**: Data lost on shutdown/crash
- **Enterprise Only**: Requires MongoDB Enterprise license
- **Memory Bound**: Dataset must fit in available RAM

**Choosing the Right Storage Engine:**

| Scenario | Recommended Engine | Reason |
|----------|-------------------|--------|
| **General Purpose** | WiredTiger | Best balance of features and performance |
| **High Concurrency** | WiredTiger | Document-level locking |
| **Storage Optimization** | WiredTiger | Compression capabilities |
| **Ultra-low Latency** | In-Memory | All data in RAM |
| **Caching Layer** | In-Memory | Fast access, data can be reconstructed |
| **Legacy Systems** | WiredTiger | MMAPv1 is deprecated |
| **Real-time Analytics** | In-Memory | Fastest possible data access |

**Performance Considerations:**

